This software performs client-side, in-browser translation of the VMware
vCenter / VCF console UI. It does not modify vCenter servers and does not
transmit page content to any server.

UI terminology is derived from VMware's official localization language packs;
the copyright of those translated strings remains with their respective owners.
"VMware", "vCenter", "vSphere", and "VCF" are trademarks of their respective
owners; this project is not affiliated with or endorsed by VMware/Broadcom.
